ll be awarded with another advancement in the plot, usually a few pages written on a \"book\".","popularity":1.0,"category":0,"themes":[1],"genres":[8],"first_release_date":665366400000,"platforms":[6],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":6,"date":665366400000,"region":8,"human":"1991-Feb-01","y":1991,"m":2}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/xf9ilgne8zjkn2zhkbfb.jpg","cloudinary_id":"xf9ilgne8zjkn2zhkbfb","width":1000,"height":1320}},{"id":50271,"name":"Metal \u0026 Lace: The Battle of the Robo Babes","slug":"metal-and-lace-the-battle-of-the-robo-babes","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/metal-and-lace-the-battle-of-the-robo-babes","created_at":1500039647604,"updated_at":1513075140062,"summary":"The year is 2053. You come to MeCha Island, home to beautiful women and deadly sports. You have $5000 cash. You decide to participate in the Robo Fighting Tournament. But the more you fight, the more you understand there is some secret connected to the very existence of MeCha island. \n \nMetal \u0026 Lace is an anime-style fighting game based on the Japanese-only NingyÅ Tsukai, with a different storyline and enhanced gameplay. In this game, you can choose between various robot models and send them into battles. All models have different names and attributes: strength, speed, etc. You can also visit shops and upgrade your mechs. Your reward is usually erotic pictures of the defeated girls.","popularity":1.0,"games":[75962,46815,75964,75858,75857,75853,68609,55058,50726,50704],"tags":[268435460],"category":0,"keywords":[78,107,343,847,970,1714,4369,4983,8218],"themes":[18,42],"genres":[4],"first_release_date":728524800000,"platforms":[6],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":6,"date":728524800000,"region":8,"human":"1993-Feb-01","y":1993,"m":2}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/sorhcg0lqsitdu5svo6l.jpg","cloudinary_id":"sorhcg0lqsitdu5svo6l","width":1000,"height":1409}},{"id":50272,"name":"Inca II: Nations of Immor