 and stronger weapons are only available for soldiers with high ranks. The basic soldier (called Cat Trooper) have no armor and is an easy prey for the bugs. Besides the experience points you gather upgrade points for your equipment for e.g. increase the damage of the weapons. Another aspect of the RPG part is that you can equip each of your soldiers individual with up to two different weapons and two tech-items (like bombs or toxic gas). \n \nThe graphic of the landscape is low on details, everything looks post apocalyptic. Much better is the combat graphic and the explosions. The cutscenes are made with the in-game graphic. Besides the sound effects your soldiers all have a voice to confirm your orders.","collection":4605,"franchise":1051,"franchises":[1051],"popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[25311,76731,68287,71455,11582,19301,25300,36950,19934,9789],"tags":[1,18,268435471,536871882,536874694,536875054,536876220,536881523],"category":0,"keywords":[970,3782,4142,5308,10611],"themes":[1,18],"genres":[15],"first_release_date":975369600000,"platforms":[6],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":6,"date":975369600000,"region":8,"human":"2000-Nov-28","y":2000,"m":11}],"screenshots":[{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/wvgvzk9nzmznb4vuyibk.jpg","cloudinary_id":"wvgvzk9nzmznb4vuyibk","width":800,"height":600},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/tkjbvh4zwatlcsrtqodr.jpg","cloudinary_id":"tkjbvh4zwatlcsrtqodr","width":800,"height":600},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/uhpedmof5ytfaxpi4xsc.jpg","cloudinary_id":"uhpedmof5ytfaxpi4xsc","width":800,"height":600}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/r7ghchn3alusezqrjm4e.jpg","cloudinary_id":"r7ghchn3alusezqrjm4e","width":613,"height":800},"esrb":{"rating":5}},{"id":50924,"name":"Sonic \u0026 Knuckles Collection","slug":"sonic-and-knuckles-collection","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/sonic-and-knuckles-collection","created_at":1500057441911,"update